name: Fantine
description:
This NFT is created from the original 3D scan of the physical sculpture of Fantine (already sold). The collector will receive a reincarnation of the Fantine as a physical unique piece (26 x 25 cm) shipped worldwide.
I like to imagine this NFT as the soul of the physical sculpture.

Contact me on socials for shipping details 
@herminebourdin

In my work I try to represent full, proud sensual women, all imbued by a strong and protective tone.
